log
@Use the fancy .In macro for includes. From Jan Klemkow. ok jmc schwarze
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: bindresvport.3,v 1.24 2010/09/07 19:52:37 schwarze Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2010, Oracle America, Inc.
